WEBVTT

1
00:00:04.439 --> 00:00:05.069
<i>Promise me you will come back.</i>

2
00:00:05.093 --> 00:00:07.181
What if I can't?

3
00:00:07.398 --> 00:00:09.966
This is definitely
the biggest movie

4
00:00:10.140 --> 00:00:12.664
that I've ever done.
in terms of its ambition.

5
00:00:12.882 --> 00:00:14.666
<i>The scale of all the sets.</i>

6
00:00:14.884 --> 00:00:17.017
and the amount of people
involved. it's just so large.

7
00:00:17.191 --> 00:00:19.671
<i>A great filmmaker
like Christopher Nolan</i>

8
00:00:19.889 --> 00:00:23.153
can do scope and action.
but also heart

