00:00:23.371 --> 00:00:24.981
<i>and humanity and rawness.</i>

10
00:00:25.155 --> 00:00:28.202
<i>This is him at his best.
going for it. you know?</i>

11
00:00:28.419 --> 00:00:30.291
Pedal to the metal.
like. we are gonna make

12
00:00:30.508 --> 00:00:34.164
the biggest and most impressive
movie that's ever been made.

13
00:00:41.041 --> 00:00:42.390
Let's go home.

14
00:00:44.696 --> 00:00:47.656
<i>"The Odyssey"
is a massive story.</i>

15
00:00:47.873 --> 00:00:48.981
And that's part
of the appeal of it.

